div.div:
Meet Punpun Punyama. Hes an average kid in an average town. He wants to win a Nobel Prize and save the world. He wants the girl he has a crush on to like him back. He wants to find some porn. Thats what he wants, but what does he get?
(Source: Viz Media)

In an age when the corners of the world have been scoured for their secrets, only one place remains unexploreda massive cave system known as the Abyss. Those who traverse its endless pits and labyrinth-like tunnels are known as Cave Raiders. A young orphan named Riko dreams of following in her mothers footsteps as a Cave Raider, and when she meets a strange robot when exploring the Abyss, shes one step closer to achieving her goal! (Source: Seven Seas Entertainment) Note: Nominated for the 11th Manga Taishou Awards (2018).
